/**
173 
 * An abstract base class that you can use to implement a new
174 
 * {@link CategoryItemRenderer}.  When you create a new
175 
 * {@link CategoryItemRenderer} you are not required to extend this class,
176 
 * but it makes the job easier.
177 
 */
178
